Class Complex

java.lang.Object
  se.miun.itm.input.model.mapping.Complex

public class Complex
extends java.lang.Object

A complex type is one that allows user defined data structures to be used instead of arrays in collection type parameter definitions. That way, arbitrary semantics can be applied when a collection of choices is added to the collection.
